price: Sila sababni Nuti qabeenyaafi ilmaan irraa isaaniif daballu (isaaniif gaarii)se’uu?
arabic: أَيَحۡسَبُونَ أَنَّمَا نُمِدُّهُم بِهِۦ مِن مَّالٖ وَبَنِينَ

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: ayaḥsabūna annamā numidduhum bihi min mālin wabanīna
